M. J. Huggins III
Executive Compensation
As Executive Vice President and Secretary; President of Commercial Banking, Secretary and Director of CresCom Bank at CAROLINA FINANCIAL CORP, M. J. Huggins III made $584,989 in total compensation.  Of this total $262,250 was received as a salary, $184,676 was received as a bonus, $19,820 was received in stock options, $30,861 was awarded as stock and $87,382 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


