Summary 



Mr. M. J. Huggins, III, is Secretary & Executive Vice President at Carolina Financial Corp., Secretary & Executive Vice President at CresCom Bank and Member-Community Bankers Counsel at South Carolina Bankers Association.He is on the Board of Directors at Renasant Bank.He received his undergraduate degree from Coastal Carolina University and an undergraduate degree from Graduate School of Banking at Louisiana State University.



